nodes.text: Trestinbinexocycline 5-Gamma was a chemical that was the primary active ingredient (1.87%) in Happy-Bore Medicated Dewormer, a dewormer designed to control and rid happabores of parasites.

Trestinbinexocycline 5-Gamma is mentioned as part of an Imperial-era Happy-Bore information and instruction pamphlet in Rey's Survival Guide, written by Jason Fry and published in 2015 as part of book releases surrounding Star Wars: The Force Awakens.
